---
import ServiceLayout from '../layouts/ServiceLayout.astro';
import { site } from '../data/site';
---

<ServiceLayout
  title="Video Inspection"
  description={`Sewer and drain video inspection services in Asheville & Hendersonville, NC. Nesbitt's Plumbing finds hard-to-diagnose problems fast. Call ${site.phone}.`}
  heroTitle="Get a Closer Look at Your Sewer Problems"
  heroSubtitle="We offer video inspections in Hendersonville and Asheville, NC."
  heroImage="/images/gallery/gallery-22.jpg"
  ctaHeading="Resolve Hard-to-Find Sewer Issues Today"
>
  <p>
    Sewer problems can be difficult to diagnose without a proper view of what's actually going on
    underneath your house. For many homeowners in Asheville and Hendersonville, NC, DIY solutions
    amount to guesswork. Get the full picture of your sewer issues with video inspection services
    from Nesbitt's Plumbing. We can shed light on your plumbing problems and find lasting
    solutions.
  </p>
  <p>Contact us now to resolve hard-to-find sewer issues in your home.</p>

  <h2 class="pt-2 text-2xl font-bold text-charcoal-900">We have the right tech for the job</h2>
  <p>
    To get to the root of your plumbing problems, we'll use a drain camera that's attached to a
    flexible line. Using the camera as a guide, our plumbers can navigate your pipes to identify
    blockages, breaks or other issues. From there, we can confidently offer plumbing repairs to
    get your system working again.
  </p>
  <p>
    Call <a href={site.phoneHref} class="font-semibold text-drop-600 hover:underline">{site.phone}</a>
    today for more information on our video inspection services.
  </p>
</ServiceLayout>
